data.description:
Tropical Paradise Home in Award Winning Wilderness Lake Preserve. Spacious and wide-open living space is one of the most distinguishing features of this gorgeous home. Its ingeniously designed floorplan features 3 Bedrooms including the great room joins together living and dining spaces that are loaded with upgrades: Extended Great Room, Upgraded Lighting, Custom built-in entertainment wall with many shelves and cubby nooks as well as a custom built-in book/display case that ads definition between the dining and living areas, custom tile floors with warm earthy tones are accented with river rock borders, attractive arched design elements. A fantastic kitchen for great entertaining includes abundant cabinetry, deep pantry, center-island, breakfast nook, stainless steel appliances and a breakfast bar / pass through window that bridges into the great room! The Owner’s Retreat is on first floor with tray ceilings, ultra large walk-in closet, walk-in shower, garden tub, and upgraded dual sink vanities.
A giant Bonus Room upstairs that is the 4th bedroom and loft rec room combo!
Outdoors living at its best with a sprawling screen enclosed patio and huge areas for everything from barbeque, sunbathing and various entertainments. 
Great location, just short walk to Wilderness Lodge, a lakeside recreation complex for the residents of Wilderness Lake which offers amazing amenities such as: Fishing docks and boats, lagoon and heated lap pools, gym with lake views, saunas, hot tub, movie theater, sports courts, game room, catering kitchen, nature center, lodge great room, parks, playgrounds, poolside barbeques, planned events and more!
Brand new roof 2023, new exterior paint 2022, new range/oven and dishwasher 2023, new bedrooms floor 2021.
